# Baked X25519 sealing secret for the warm enclave image. Generated by
# deliver.py keygen, COPYed into the (private, attestation-gated) image at build,
# read by enc_fetch._enclave_secret() when ENCLAVE_ENC_SECRET is unset. The
# matching pubkey is the bounty's enclaveEncPub. NEVER committed -- the live image
# layer is the only place the secret lives, behind a private repo + CS attestation.
enclave_enc_secret
